verbose_text: Even distinctions between Pi pools in mitochondrial, intracellular and extracellular compartments are visible due to their characteristic pH and thereby peak position in the 31 P MR spectrum.7 Over the past decades, studies have observed small alterations in 31 P MRS signal levels or pH changes in the brain during activation.8, 9, 10, 11, 12, 13, 14, 15, 16 However, these small changes are in marked contrast to the large activation induced alterations of 31 P MR signals in muscle.
